 at escalating concentrations progressively decreased VÎ», and VF became sustained, when tissue volume/VÎ» was above safety factor Îº=4.4Â±0.6 (n=9) during rapid pacing. Treatment with glybenclamide decreased VT/VÎ» below Îº at any pacing rate and prevented VF sustainability. CONCLUSIONS Sustained VF was only sustained in ventricular volume exceeding critical VÎ»=Î»LÃ—Î»TVÃ—Î»TM.},
